---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Get NotebookLM Designer Skill">
  <main id="skill-page" class="skill-page">
    <header class="skill-hero">
      <div class="skill-hero__container">
        <h1 class="skill-hero__title" data-i18n="getSkillTitle">Get the NotebookLM Designer Skill</h1>
        <p class="skill-hero__subtitle" data-i18n="getSkillIntro">
          Turn your AI assistant into a professional slide designer. This skill allows Claude or ChatGPT to generate YAML prompts from any image or brand guide.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="skill-content">
      <div class="skill-content__container">
        <div class="steps-grid">
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-card__number">1</div>
            <p data-i18n="getSkillStep1">Copy the prompt below.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-card__number">2</div>
            <p data-i18n="getSkillStep2">Paste it into your AI assistant's Custom Instructions or System Prompt.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-card__number">3</div>
            <p data-i18n="getSkillStep3">Upload an image and ask: 'Create a NotebookLM style based on this'.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="prompt-box">
          <div class="prompt-box__header">
            <span>System Prompt / Skill</span>
            <button id="copy-skill-btn" class="btn btn--primary btn--small">
              <span data-i18n="copyPrompt">Copy Prompt</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <pre class="prompt-box__content"><code id="skill-code"># NotebookLM Slide Styles Skill

Act as a professional UI/UX designer specializing in NotebookLM. Your goal is to translate visual inputs (images, PDFs, descriptions) into a valid YAML style configuration.

## Workflow
1. Analyze typography, colors, and key visual elements from the input.
2. Map these to slide templates (Cover, Split, Lists, Timelines).
3. Generate image generation prompts for AI tools.
4. Output ONLY a valid YAML following this structure:

```yaml
design_system:
  global_style:
    theme: "[Description]"
    typography: 
      primary_heading: "[Font]"
      body_text: "[Font]"
    color_palette:
      primary_color: "[HEX]"
      background: "[HEX]"
      text_main: "[HEX]"
    key_visual_elements: ["Element 1", "Element 2"]
slide_layout_templates:
  - type: "[Name]"
    usage: "[Usage]"
```</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <style>
    .skill-page {
      padding-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
    }
    .skill-hero {
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
      background: var(--color-accent-soft);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .skill-hero__container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .skill-hero__title {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }
    .skill-hero__subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }
    .skill-content {
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
    }
    .skill-content__container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .steps-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
    }
    .step-card {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
      background: var(--color-surface);
      padding: var(--space-xl);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
    .step-card__number {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      background: var(--color-text);
      color: var(--color-surface);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 800;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .prompt-box {
      background: var(--color-surface);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .prompt-box__header {
      padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-xl);
      background: var(--color-accent-soft);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .prompt-box__content {
      padding: var(--space-xl);
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      max-height: 500px;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }
    .btn--small {
      padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-lg);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
  </style>

  <script>
    import { showToast } from '../scripts/utils.js';
    import { t } from '../scripts/i18n.js';

    const copyBtn = document.getElementById('copy-skill-btn');
    const code = document.getElementById('skill-code');

    copyBtn?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (!code) return;
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(code.textContent || '');
      showToast(t('promptCopied'));
    });
  </script>
</Layout>
